1759
01:59:30.528 --> 01:59:32.360
- Uh. that's me.
- Stand by. It's kind of a lot.

1760
01:59:32.496 --> 01:59:34.997
TD. what are
your playback channels?

1761
01:59:35.133 --> 01:59:36.835
They're in W. X. Y and Z.

1762
01:59:36.970 --> 01:59:38.533
We're gonna load up all of them.

1763
01:59:38.668 --> 01:59:40.502
It's coming in raw.
so you got to mix it.

1764
01:59:40.637 --> 01:59:42.734
And. hey. no tape delay.
I mean. not a frame.

1765
01:59:42.870 --> 01:59:44.335
Go straight to the feed
and leave it open.

1766
01:59:44.470 --> 01:59:45.974
Director. no cuts.

1767
01:59:46.109 --> 01:59:47.476
This plays itself.

1768
01:59:47.611 --> 01:59:48.872
It's gonna go outside
your market fast.

1769
01:59:49.007 --> 01:59:50.474
How do I route
from the affiliate server

1770
01:59:50.609 --> 01:59:52.075
so network has access?

1771
01:59:52.210 --> 01:59:53.510
You really think network's
gonna bump World War III

1772
01:59:53.645 --> 01:59:55.148
for whatever you got?

